The,ChatBottle,API,allows,developers,to,discover,the,best,chat,bots,and,to,make,their,own,bots,more,discoverable,By,integrating,their,bots,with,the,API,developers,can,get,data,about,how,and,how,much,people,use,them,ChatBottle,gets,notified,whenever,a,bot,sends,or,receives,a,message,and,can,rank,bots,based,on,their,usage,data